{"tid":779044,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"招新手一齊踢波","createTime":"2018-08-14T06:52:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-20T03:35:11.000Z","uid":92200,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6b3ebd6030cbcc1800d3bd702d6d063af7f157c1","tid":779044,"uid":92200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T06:52:32.000Z","msg":"過去已經係高登連登攪咗兩年足球隊，好多巴打開始返工返學，出席率開始少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以係時侯搵新血加入<br />\n每次招親都有人問隊友出黎會唔會好似C7 美斯，我可以話無，大家都係踢得麻麻但至在做運動同練下波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我地有個教練會從中提點下 同指導下，希望開心之多餘又可以提升返實力<br />\n總之無壓力的，但要守紀律就可以<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家唔介意我社工攪呢隊波，即管填表，會再搵你傾傾<br />\n<br />\n年紀唔想有太大差距，所以希望24歲或以下<br />\n如果真係過24又想一齊踢，我會MARK低的，有空缺會叫你地<br />\n我地多數星期一至六 揀一日黎踢 (視乎有冇場)<br />\n暫時我地多數7點-9點 係九龍灣區踢<br />\n<br />\n有興趣填表先<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdIXO6DEzAfgKHQrvGONDSdA7nBrDpQPso-GCJ8SJSoAO07Tw/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSdIXO6DEzAfgKHQrvGONDSdA7nBrDpQPso-GCJ8SJSoAO07Tw%2Fviewform&d=ZKH8qiq0938nELvGat%2FllJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=cc446322\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdIXO6DEzAfgKHQrvGONDSdA7nBrDpQPso-GCJ8SJSoAO07Tw/viewform</a><br />\n<br />\n但要提醒返，每次填表都超過成百人<br />\n我地無可能踢哂 所以點都會揀返合適既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6daa4c16c4a19db79cd50260cf49ceb20ef47249","tid":779044,"uid":80332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T06:55:21.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"ef85f15e3b0ce39aae08b78b85da5c045a3c3a6a","tid":779044,"uid":65030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T15:59:02.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"6ecb2106984b7a42895dc7b6ba2d1383918d26cd","tid":779044,"uid":130283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T18:10:16.000Z","msg":"踢一兩個月得唔得？ 外國讀書撚"},{"pid":"e35dd3304b033890707603abdfb6b475b75f8d2b","tid":779044,"uid":26341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T18:08:24.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"8a05fbed24af628342c9207dd9c27c09d0209e28","tid":779044,"uid":65030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T00:26:35.000Z","msg":"填左表，無加我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f091962107cf8231684ae789113da56bd648596e","tid":779044,"uid":92200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T03:35:11.000Z","msg":"推  再招人補給<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}